<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-05T10:00:00-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-05T10:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-05T10:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Insomniac Games 如何尝试为各种玩家制作蜘蛛侠套装</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;迈尔斯·莫拉莱斯在电子游戏《蜘蛛侠 2》中穿着穿越蜘蛛侠套装的静态照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XlGJRN7B00PRfZ80E07y3J9xJk4=/300x0:3540x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72830940/IMG_6832.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;迈尔斯·莫拉莱斯 (Miles Morales) 穿着“穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙”套装。&lt;/em>; |图片：索尼互动娱乐&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;s2P8Ca&quot;>;对于 Insomniac Games 的艺术团队来说，似乎每个人都想要一份工作：制作蜘蛛侠的套装。自从&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/4/17817392/sp​​ider-man-marvel-ps4-review&quot;>;第一款&lt;em>;蜘蛛侠&lt;/em>;游戏在高级艺术总监 Jacinda Chew 表示，在 PS4 上为游戏中的服装建模一直是工作室角色团队中“竞争激烈的任务”。在三款游戏的过程中，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23915605/spider-man-2-review-ps5&quot;>;最近推出的&lt;em>;蜘蛛侠2&lt;/em>; &lt;/a>;，团队成功添加了大量可解锁的套装，涵盖了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23743489/spider-man-across-the-spider-verse- review-sony-marvel&quot;>;&lt;em>;穿越蜘蛛侠&lt;/em>;动画电影&lt;/a>;至&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/15/21517350/ Spider-man-miles-morales-spider-cat-backpack-sidekick-video&quot;>;互联网上最受欢迎的杂货店猫&lt;/a>;。 “这就是一种享受，”Chew 说，“能够制作一套西装。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WQJFok&quot;>;但是，这从一开始对她来说并不是显而易见的事情。 Chew 说，直到第一个&lt;em>;蜘蛛侠&lt;/em>;推出并且......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11 /5/23945063/spider-man-2-ps5-insomniac-suits&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/5/23945063/spider-man-2-ps5-insomniac-suits" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/5/23945063/spider-man-2-ps5-insomniac-suits</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-05T08:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-05T08:00:00-05:00</updated><title>人工智能如何让披头士乐队再次重聚</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;安装程序徽标的全黑版本。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3xHE-JjxU2ioLMi2FBF3xns0tbA=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72830656/Installer_Site_Post_002.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：William Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;F7iDCb&quot;>;嗨，朋友们！欢迎来到&lt;em>;Installer&lt;/em>; No. 13，这是世界上最好的、&lt;em>;边缘&lt;/em>;最前沿的东西的指南。 （如果您是新来的，欢迎，很高兴您找到了我们，您也可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/installer-newsletter&quot;>;&lt;em>; 阅读所有旧版本安装程序&lt;/em>;主页&lt;/a>;。）&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;gJfqra&quot;>;本周，我一直在观看&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/913290 -barbarian?language=en-US&quot;>;&lt;em>;&lt;strong>;野蛮人&lt;/strong>;&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/884605-no -hard-feelings?language=en-US&quot;>;&lt;em>;&lt;strong>;没有难受的感觉&lt;/strong>;&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，阅读&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/gabor /from-t2-to-pebble-the-rise-challenges-and-lessons-of-building-a-twitter-alternative-553652f1d1e7&quot;>;&lt;strong>;构建“下一个 Twitter”的挑战&lt;/strong>;&lt;/ a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://variety.com/2023/film/features/marvel-jonathan-majors-problem-the-marvels-reshoots-kang-1235774940/&quot;>;&lt;strong>;漫威复杂的未来&lt;/ strong>;&lt;/a>;，使用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://pager.xyz/&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Pager&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; 来理解我的所有屏幕截图，并向所有人发送 &lt;a href= “https://nautil.us/my-brain-doesnt-picture-things-407444/&quot;>;&lt;strong>;这篇关于失语症的文章&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;解释一下，不，我真的看不到图片在我的脑海里，是的，这很疯狂，不，我什至没有意识到其他人可以做到这一点。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;M1k5XB&quot;>;我还为您提供了一些漂亮的人工智能工具、机器人真空吸尘器、一堆有关披头士乐队新歌的新东西、辛普森一家 GIF...&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/5/23945399/beatles-ai-fortnite-og-macbook-pro-installer-newsletter&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/5/23945399/beatles-ai-fortnite-og-macbook-pro-installer-newsletter" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/5/23945399/beatles-ai-fortnite-og-macbook-pro-installer-newsletter</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-05T06:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-05T06:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Epic 诉 Google，解释</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 徽标和 Epic Games 徽标经过 Photoshop 处理到大富翁棋盘上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/px5qxPX59hsh1jDJRk_fWv-gDxY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72830431/236883_Epic_Vs_Google_A_CVirginia。 0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;关于 11 月 6 日开始的大型应用商店试用您需要了解的一切。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23944251/epic-google-antitrust-trial-explainer-monopoly&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23944251/epic-google-antitrust-trial-explainer-monopoly" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23944251/epic-google-antitrust-trial-explainer-monopoly</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T18:34:31-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T18:34:31-04:00</updated><title> Discord 文件链接将在对抗恶意软件一天后过期</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/b2foMXN6WLx75wkqUULWNH1LHG0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72829514 /acastro_STK062_03.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;w4w2gQ&quot;>;任何使用 Discord 托管文件的人都会想要更改这一点，因为链接到今年年底，这些文件将开始每 24 小时刷新一次。该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/discord-will-switch-to-temporary-file-links-to-block-malware-delivery/&quot;>;告诉&lt;em>;Bleeping计算机&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;这样做将帮助公司对抗在其平台上传播的恶意软件，因为这使其更有能力“限制对标记内容的访问”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;mIpaJb&quot;>;根据这篇文章，Discord 表示这一变化不会影响任何在平台上共享内容的人，因为客户端内的链接将自动刷新。但是，在 Discord 之外共享的链接在重新生成一天后将无法使用。该公司表示，将在“未来几周内”与开发者分享更多信息，他们“可能会看到最小的影响。”&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot; JzZlOx&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;PC 流媒体服务 Shadow 披露安全漏洞&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23915206/shadow-pc-streaming-service-security-breach&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= “JYWAfq&quot;>;正如&lt;em>;Bleeping Computer&lt;/em>;所说，网络安全公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.trellix.com/about/newsroom/stories/research/discord-i-want-to-play -a-game/&quot;>;Trellix...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946640/discord-file-links -will-expire-after-a-day-to-fight-malware&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946640/discord-file-links-will-expire-after-a-day-to-fight-malware" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946640/discord-file-links-will-expire-after-a-day-to-fight-malware</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T18:17:13-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T18:17:13-04:00</updated><title>人工智能公司有各种各样的理由反对为受版权保护的内容付费</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色背景上显示大脑图形的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MZKtpwVgEqfDWc7lcFlccAn4zIE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72829494/acastro_181017_1777_brain_ai_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mnOwg0&quot;>;美国版权Office 正在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.regulations.gov/document/COLC-2023-0006-0001/comment&quot;>;就生成性的潜在新规则&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/23444685/generative-ai-copyright-infringement-legal-fair-use-training-data&quot;>;人工智能对受版权保护的材料的使用&lt;/a>;，世界上最大的人工智能公司有很多说。我们从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117934-meta&quot;>;Meta&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/ document/24117935-google&quot;>;Google&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117936-microsoft&quot;>;微软&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117931-adobe&quot;>;Adobe&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117933-hugging-face&quot;>;拥抱脸&lt;/a>;、 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117937-stabilityai-stable-diffusion-etc&quot;>;StabilityAI&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/ Documents/24117938-anthropic&quot;>;Anthropic&lt;/a>; 下面，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24117932-apple&quot;>;Apple&lt;/a>; 的回应，重点关注对人工智能编写的代码进行版权保护。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;018SLN&quot;>;他们的方法存在一些差异，但大多数人的总体信息是相同的：他们认为自己不应该付费来训练人工智能模型关于受版权保护的作品。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;PywpRo&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;关于人工智能版权的可怕事实是没有人知道接下来会发生什么&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23444685/generative-ai-copyright-infringement -legal-fair-use-training-data&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bing、Bard 和 ChatGPT：人工智能如何重写互联网&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23610427 /chatbots-chatgpt-new-bing-google-bard-conversational-ai&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;C1Y3lN&quot;>;版权局 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/29/23851126/us-copyright-office-ai-public-comments&quot;>;8月30日开放意见征询期&lt;/a>;，截止日期为10月18日关于正在考虑围绕使用受版权保护的数据进行更改的书面评论...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946353/generative-ai -copyright-training-data-openai-microsoft-google-meta-stabilityai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946353/generative-ai-copyright-training-data-openai-microsoft-google-meta-stabilityai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946353/generative-ai-copyright-training-data-openai-microsoft-google-meta-stabilityai</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T16:31:42-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T16:31:42-04:00</updated><title> 《堡垒之夜》舞蹈动作的版权之争又卷土重来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/K2AILwvzesQDkmioxcGlaJCj94c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72829255/acastro_STK108__03.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yENUbg&quot;>;本周，美国上诉法院法官组成的小组重新启动了针对 &lt;em>;Fortnite 的法律战&lt;/em>;通过逆转&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gamesindustry.biz/lawsuit-over-fortnite-dance-dismissed-by-court&quot;>;驳回&lt;/a>;诉讼&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/choreographer-sues-epic-fortnite-emote-kyle-hanagami-rcna23075&quot;>;去年&lt;/a>;由专业编舞者 Kyle Hanagami 针对 Epic Games 提交。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/choreographer-epic-games-copyright-lawsuit-revived-new-ruling-1235461441/amp/&quot;>;&lt;em>;广告牌&lt;/em>;&lt; /a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;指出&lt;a href=&quot;https://cdn.ca9.uscourts.gov/datastore/opinions/2023/11/01/22-55890.pdf&quot;>;提交的意见11 月 1 日&lt;/a>; (PDF)，美国第九巡回上诉法院法官理查德·佩兹 (Richard Paez) 写道，即使舞蹈的个别元素不能受版权保护，但编排却可以。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;66t1F2&quot; >;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nypost.com/2022/08/31/lawsuit-against-fortnite-developer-over-its-complicated-dance-dismissed-by-judge/&quot;>;下级法院表示&lt;/ a>; 舞蹈作品由无法单独保护的姿势组成。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;i4S7yY&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;史诗般的表情辩论：有关 Fortnite 正在进行的舞蹈诉讼的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/1/15/18184401/ epic-games-fortnite-dance-emote-legal-lawsuit-2-milly-carlton-floss&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Fortnite 的新赛季是一次穿越游戏历史的旅行&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2023/11/3/23943701/fortnite-og-new-season-tilted-towers-baller&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= “EFkA0D&quot;>;它发现&lt;em>;Fortnite&lt;/em>;中角色所使用的舞蹈编排的步骤和姿势“除了四个相同的姿势之外”并不“基本相似”，因为他们“没有共享任何创意”元素”...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23946260/epic-fortnite-choreography-emote-lawsuit-ruling-overturned</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T10:43:05-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T10:43:05-04:00</updated><title>索尼的降噪 XM5 价格达到了迄今为​​止的最低价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人从棕褐色皮革钱包中取出银色索尼 WH-1000XM5 耳机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UUMXtF9_9MfTNJSxQlr4b9oz3Dg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828481/DSCF7932.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;WH-1000XM5s 仍然是您能买到的最好的耳机，即使索尼的命名约定仍然很糟糕。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;dTFUFU&quot;>;无论您是父母、经常旅行还是被迫出行的人，平静与安宁都很难获得聆听正在进行的建设，感觉像是永恒的——相信我，我会知道的。值得庆幸的是，&lt;strong>;索尼的 WH-1000XM5&lt;/strong>; 目前&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09XS7JWHH/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target= &quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckTQYqEzFSW&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target。 com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fsony-wh-1000xm5-bluetooth-wireless-noise-canceling-headphones%2F-%2FA-86777236&amp;amp;sharedid =theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目标&lt;/a>;低至 328 美元（折扣 73 美元），与迄今为止的最优惠价格相符。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c -float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;AmJzoV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;: “我们将顶级 ANC 耳机送到实验室测试其降噪能力”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/23852015/active-noise-cancellation-headphone-test-audio-lab” },{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年 PC 礼品指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content -creator-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您已经可以获得的最佳早期黑色星期五科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black -friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;UgJXFZ&quot;>;索尼旗舰耳机提供了一些自六年多前 1000X 系列问世以来，您可以在耳罩式耳机中获得最佳音质。此后，竞争变得越来越激烈 - 以最近发布的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23920591/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-headphones-review&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra&lt;/a>; 为例举个例子，但最新版本继续提供一流的 ANC 和清晰、自然的音频......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945130/sony-wh-1000xm5-amazon-fire-tv-soundbar-meross-smart-plug-deal-sale</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</updated><title> Echo Show 8 仍然是智能显示器中的佼佼者</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;增强的声音、小部件和 Thread 收音机是对亚马逊最好的带屏幕智能扬声器的良好（但不华丽）升级。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23945192/amazon-echo-show-8-alexa-smart-display-review</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:30:00-04:00</updated><title>如何设置 Echo Show 以向您展示最少的垃圾内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量图显示亚马逊 Echo 智能扬声器和显示器的不同方面。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tpdWk33pduMLms88izz95t7JhAM=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828256/HT006_ALEXA_ECHO_SHOW_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊的 Echo Show 是一款更好的智能显示器，没有亚马逊的所有东西。&lt;/em>; | The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cYV50E&quot;>;亚马逊的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/23709233&quot;>;Echo Show 智能显示器&lt;/a>;确实很棒设备。价格介于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09B2SRGXH?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;90 美元&lt;/a>; 至 &lt;a href= &quot;https://www.amazon.com/echo-show-10/dp/B07VHZ41L8?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;250 美元&lt;/a>;（通常更便宜）亚马逊的永久销售），你会得到一个带有触摸屏的智能扬声器，可以播放音乐，向你展示照片，与朋友和家人进行视频通话，充当安全摄像头，兼作 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.aboutamazon.com/news/devices/connect-alexa-bluetooth&quot;>;蓝牙扬声器&lt;/a>;，并控制您的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door -lock&quot;>;智能锁&lt;/a>;、灯和安全摄像头。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7dS6QY&quot;>;但是，有一个很大的警告：亚马逊的硬件受到其服务的大力补贴，当您购买Echo Show，您实质上是将亚马逊服务的小广告牌带入您的家中。如果您按开箱即用的方式使用它，您将受到大量臃肿软件的轰炸，鼓励您使用亚马逊的服务，您很可能会想拔掉它......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23944889/set-up-echo-show-without-amazon-ads-how-to</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-04T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-11-04T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>萨姆·班克曼·弗里德可能不是最后一个加密货币罪犯</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Sam Bankman-Fried 在翻滚的加密货币图形背景前的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wcQHUB-4hEdJN7mJXtcgrTOB2K0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72828126/236817_SBF_Trial_Stock_CVirginia_ SKETCHES_15.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 提供 |摄影：彭博社、盖蒂图片社&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;加密货币倡导者可能认为 FTX 的崩溃是一种反常现象，但他们可能很难说服公众相信这一点。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/4/23945602/sam-bankman-fried-guilty-verdict-ftx-crypto-industry-impact</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>